  <chunk id="b0718d5c8888216c95fa19d7a79fd709da2c3ff4.c2" text="Conclusions: Severe VZV-CAP is responsible for an acute pulmonary involvement associated with a significant morbidity and mortality. Steroid therapy did not influence mortality, but increased the risk of superinfection.">
